      "title": "Dakuten in Katakana",
      "body": "Dakuten (゛) works the same way in katakana — the two small marks voice the consonant:\n\nカ → ガ (ka → ga)\nサ → ザ (sa → za)\nタ → ダ (ta → da)\nハ → バ (ha → ba)"
